hackathon-description-text: This is a standard hackathon format with a few twists. Its during the day on Saturday and Sunday, not 24 consecutive hours. It all ends with a showcase event, and prizes will be awarded by our sponsors.
hackathon-eligibility: No requirements. All are welcome, from the experienced hacker to the newbie wannabe. Registration may close early though if demand is high.

hackathon-prizes.prize-title: Best use of online / cloud application

hackathon-description-header: This is a hacking session in which participants will conceptualize, create and present their projects. Anything goes as long as its music and/or audio related.
